The purpose of this project is to create a library that can be used for connecting a ZF 1.x project to Jira 4.4+ through OAuth and the API.

For reference on how to setup an API connection, 
	http://docs.atlassian.com/jira/REST/latest/
	https://developer.atlassian.com/display/JIRADEV/JIRA+REST+API+Example+-+OAuth+authentication
	
This project will continue to evolve while as my development needs grow.  Please feel free to contribute and i will make sure to merge your forked changes into the mainline.